      • getRegexMarkerFilter

        TextMarkerFilter getRegexMarkerFilter(List<MarkerFilterType> types,
                                    String regex,
                                    int blockSize)
        For a given regex, finds any matches within the text, and adds the appropriate marker to these matches. The markers will automatically be added to the last group indicated in the regex, or to the entire regex if it contains no groups.

      • getRegexMarkerFilter

        TextMarkerFilter getRegexMarkerFilter(List<MarkerFilterType> types,
                                    String regex,
                                    int groupIndex,
                                    int blockSize)
        For a given regex, finds any matches within the text, and adds the appropriate marker to these matches. The markers will be added for the group indicated by the groupIndex.
